quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"Mazitshabalale zombini izandla zika-Abû Lahab, (naye) atshabalale"
  111,2,Ubutyebi bakhe nabantwana bakhe bungamncedi nganto
  111,3,Uza kutsha edangatyeni loMlilo odwanguzayo
  111,4,"Nomfazi wakhe, umthwalikazi weenkuni"
  111,5,Entanyeni yakhe uya kuqanyangelwa ngentambo yomthi wesundu